import React from "react"
import { Box, Flex ,Stack} from "@chakra-ui/layout"
import { Image,Heading  } from "@chakra-ui/react"
export const TravelPlan=()=>{
    return(
        <>
         <Flex justifyContent="center" flexDirection="column">
             <Image src="https://www.thexpressng.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/SriLanka_Slider.jpg" alt="Segun Adebayo"  height="400px" width="100%" objectFit="cover"/>
             <Heading marginX="auto" marginTop="-350px" boxShadow="dark-lg" borderRadius="5px" padding="10px">3 Day Trip in Sri Lanka</Heading>
             <Stack direction="row" spacing={4} align="center"></Stack>

        </Flex>
       \
         
        </>
    )
}
